<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hinkhuo thak mel a kidang hi,
 Hukdampa ka muh in;
 A Kross-ah lungsietna ka mui,
 Ka Hukdampa zainem chuh.

[V2]
 Ginlah leh lauh abei tai,
 Isu'n thim A salhvak tai;
 Van chung gam naiin a lang,
 Hukdampa ka muh ni'n.

[V3]
 2. A hehpihna mak chun ei hawl,
 Ka Hukdampa ka mui;
 A Hukdamna thu hun tunin,
 Ka hukdampa deihum chun.

[V4]
 3. Buoina meipi chuh zing mahleh,
 Hukdampa ka mu tai;
 Mulo mahleng ei umpih zing,
 Ka Hukdampa a um zing.

[V5]
 4. Dettak in ka khut in ei tui,
 Hukdampa ka muh ni'n;
 Lalchutphah lamah ei pui hi,
 Ziechun Hukdampa mu'ng ka.</lyrics>
<title>SINCE I FOUND MY SAVIOUR</title>
<hymn_number>345</hymn_number>
</song>